                <Sentence Num="6" WritingMode="vertical">（六）　窒素プラズマアーク</Sentence>
                <Sentence Num="7" WritingMode="vertical">（七）　水素及び二酸化炭素との化学反応</Sentence>
                <Sentence Num="8" WritingMode="vertical">（八）　過熱蒸気反応</Sentence>
